query:
SELECT 
  i.id as inventoryId,
  i.productId,
  p.sku,
  p.description,
  i.quantity,
  i.reservedQuantity,
  (i.quantity - i.reservedQuantity) as available,
  wl.code as locationCode,
  wz.code as zoneCode
FROM inventory i
JOIN products p ON p.id = i.productId
JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON wl.id = i.locationId
JOIN warehouseZones wz ON wz.id = wl.zoneId
WHERE i.reservedQuantity > 0
AND wz.code = 'EXP'
ORDER BY i.id DESC
LIMIT 10;
